OL,3,CLeft behind in Afghanistan: Tales from
OL,4,Cbehind Taliban lines
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Producer Luke Cullen
OL,8,F"I strongly believe that the leak has
OL,9,Fmade it significantly easier for them
OL,10,Fto identify and locate us."
OL,12,FThese are the words of an Afghan who
OL,13,Fworked for the UK in the country
OL,14,Fbefore the Taliban swept back to power
OL,15,Fin August 2021.
OL,17,FFollowing the chaotic evacuations from
OL,18,FKabul in the same month, many Afghans
OL,19,Fwho had worked for the UK government
OL,20,Fwere left behind.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
