OL,3,CLeft behind in Afghanistan: Tales from
OL,4,Cbehind Taliban lines
OL,6,FThe government set up the Afghan
OL,7,FRelocations and Assistance Policy
OL,8,F(Arap) to try and evacuate those
OL,9,Fdeemed at serious risk from the
OL,10,FTaliban due to their association with
OL,11,Fthe UK.
OL,13,FHowever, a dataset that contained the
OL,14,Fpersonal information of nearly 19,000
OL,15,Fpeople who applied to Arap was
OL,16,Freleased "in error" in February 2022
OL,17,Fby a defence official.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
