OL,6,FThe Ministry of Defence only became
OL,7,Faware of the breach after excerpts of
OL,8,Fthe dataset were posted anonymously on
OL,9,Fa Facebook group in August 2023.
OL,11,FA superinjunction was then granted at
OL,12,Fthe High Court in an attempt to
OL,13,Fprevent the Taliban from finding out
OL,14,Fabout the leak.
OL,16,FThe super-injunction was lifted on
OL,17,FTuesday, following a review, and the
OL,18,Fpeople involved were contacted by
OL,19,Femail, warning them of the potential
OL,20,Fdanger.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
