OL,3,CLeft behind in Afghanistan: Tales from
OL,4,Cbehind Taliban lines
OL,6,FITV News has been speaking to people,
OL,7,Fboth inside Afghanistan and in the UK,
OL,8,Fabout the "life or death" risk this
OL,9,Fhas caused them, their relatives and
OL,10,Ffriends.
OL,12,FA message from Afghanistan
OL,14,FPart of a voicenote sent to ITV News
OL,15,Ffrom inside Afghanistan.
OL,17,FITV News has been in contact with an
OL,18,Findividual who is still inside
OL,19,FAfghanistan, on the run from the
OL,20,FTaliban.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
