OL,3,CLeft behind in Afghanistan: Tales from
OL,4,Cbehind Taliban lines
OL,6,FFor security reasons, we are unable to
OL,7,Fsay exactly what their role was, but
OL,8,Fthey worked for the UK in Afghanistan.
OL,10,FThey told us, via voicenote, that
OL,11,Fdespite the precautions they have
OL,12,Ftaken since 2021, this leak may have
OL,13,Fput them in direct danger.
OL,15,FThey said: "Yesterday I received an
OL,16,Femail that our data was leaked in
OL,17,F2022, mistakenly.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
