OL,3,CLeft behind in Afghanistan: Tales from
OL,4,Cbehind Taliban lines
OL,6,F"We have been extremely cautious about
OL,7,Four safety over the past four years.
OL,8,FDespite our efforts, my family and I
OL,9,Fhave received multiple threats through
OL,10,Fsocial media and direct calls," they
OL,11,Fexplained.
OL,13,FThey added: "I cannot confirm
OL,14,Fcertainly that the Taliban used the
OL,15,Fdata leaked from the UK side, but I
OL,16,Fstrongly believe that the leak has
OL,17,Fmade it significantly easier for them
OL,18,Fto identify and locate us."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
