OL,3,CLeft behind in Afghanistan: Tales from
OL,4,Cbehind Taliban lines
OL,6,F"Despite receiving approval from the
OL,7,FUK for relocation, the process is
OL,8,Fmoving slowly and we are still under
OL,9,Fthreat," they finished as the
OL,10,Fvoicenote crackled and went silent.
OL,12,FSiblings disunited
OL,14,FTamanna has now safely relocated to
OL,15,Fthe north of England.
OL,17,FBut her brother is now in graver
OL,18,Fdanger in Afghanistan.
OL,20,FHe worked in the country as a military
OL,21,Fofficer alongside the UK government.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
