OL,3,CLeft behind in Afghanistan: Tales from
OL,4,Cbehind Taliban lines
OL,6,FTamanna says they are in constant
OL,7,Fcontact because of the serious nature
OL,8,Fof the danger now posed to him because
OL,9,Fof the data leak.
OL,11,FShe said: "We're talking about these
OL,12,Fthings a little bit every minute or
OL,13,Fevery second because it's a serious
OL,14,Fthing."
OL,16,FShe described that he was feeling
OL,17,F"frustrated and anxious".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
