OL,3,CLeft behind in Afghanistan: Tales from
OL,4,Cbehind Taliban lines
OL,6,F"It was really a shock for him because
OL,7,Fhe already had his concerns and
OL,8,Ftensions about the safety and security
OL,9,Fof my family and threats he is facing
OL,10,Ffor the last four years", she said.
OL,12,FTamanna said her brother had already
OL,13,Frequested support and help to remain
OL,14,Fsafe, but delays in the system and now
OL,15,Fthis data leak have left her feeling
OL,16,Feven more concerned.
OL,18,F"I am here, I cannot do anything and
OL,19,Fthey are in a bad situation."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
