OL,3,CLeft behind in Afghanistan: Tales from
OL,4,Cbehind Taliban lines
OL,6,FShe bemoaned the lack of government
OL,7,Fhelp, saying: "I don't know from which
OL,8,Fsource I should get help? I should
OL,9,Ftalk with who? And how can I get
OL,10,Fsupport?"
OL,12,FQuestions for the government
OL,14,FITV News also spoke to Khadija - not
OL,15,Fher real name - who was working with
OL,16,Fthe UK government in Afghanistan
OL,17,Fbefore being evacuated under the Arap
OL,18,Fscheme.
OL,20,F"This issue is the most awful time in
OL,21,Fmy life," she said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
