OL,3,CLeft behind in Afghanistan: Tales from
OL,4,Cbehind Taliban lines
OL,6,FShe explained that because of the leak
OL,7,F"right now, me, my husband, my
OL,8,Fchildren, my mom, my sisters, my
OL,9,Fbrother, they are all in direct danger
OL,10,Fbecause everyone has their data".
OL,12,FShe still has a large number of family
OL,13,Fmembers in Afghanistan, including
OL,14,Fparents-in-law, aunts, uncles and
OL,15,Fcousins, who were all implicated in
OL,16,Fthe data leak.
OL,18,FThe two cousins are still teenagers
OL,19,Fand moving about rural areas to stay
OL,20,Fsafe. They can't stay with family for
OL,21,Ffear of being identified.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
