OL,6,FThe personal information of nearly
OL,7,F19,000 people who applied for the
OL,8,FAfghan Relocations and Assistance
OL,9,FPolicy (Arap) was released "in error"
OL,10,Fin 2022, ITV News' Political
OL,11,FCorrespondent Carl Dinnen reports
OL,13,FKhadija said she didn't dare tell them
OL,14,Fabout the data leak in case it put
OL,15,Fthem in more trouble.
OL,17,F"The only thing I mentioned to them
OL,18,Fwas please, please change your phone
OL,19,Fnumber if you can. Change your house
OL,20,Fagain and don't go out alone."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
