OL,3,CLeft behind in Afghanistan: Tales from
OL,4,Cbehind Taliban lines
OL,6,FKhadija also says she regrets trusting
OL,7,Fthe UK government.
OL,9,F"Right now, every day, I mean every
OL,10,Fminute from yesterday to right now, I
OL,11,Fregret and just blame myself for
OL,12,Ftrusting the government."
OL,14,FShe concluded: "If you have a law, you
OL,15,Fneed to follow the law. If the law
OL,16,Fsays that there is a data breach, you
OL,17,Fneed to inform the person. Why didn't
OL,18,Fyou inform everyone at the beginning?"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
